phpShop is a free PHP-based e-commerce application developed by
Edikon?. phpShop allows you to setup an online store and manage all aspects
of your online business by using a web browser.

phpShop was designed as a tool to offer easy customization and a standardized
platform for development of e-commerce applications. Its use of open source
technoligies allows for cross platform deployment using any operating system
that support PHP.

phpShop is distributed under the General Public License (GPL). You can
Download phpShop for free.

You can view a list of Live Sites that are running live sites. If you site
uses phpShop, please be sure to add your site to the list!

